Comment: 0,0:02:51.07,0:02:54.70,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5\fad(100,150)\3c&H000000&}bear witness to my song
Comment: 0,0:02:54.99,0:02:59.28,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5\fad(100,150)\3c&H000000&}Your heart contains all its truth
Comment: 0,0:02:59.49,0:03:02.16,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5\fad(100,150)\3c&H000000&}Even when all you see in your path are storms
